      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4437 - And it is narrated from Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub, from Malik ibn Atiyyah, from Abu Abdullah (as) who said:\n\"A woman cannot be married alongside her maternal aunt, but the maternal aunt can be married alongside the daughter of her sister.\""
